author: @anastasiagraham2418
text:
My theory is that Jaehyun’s number 1 passion is his work (CLUE: how meticulous he is in the kitchen) So he never makes time for his gf and she was upset bc of it. Eventually they broke up 

Life goes on but one day, he got the text and he realizes he misses her too (CLUE: Can We Go Back in the background) At first he was unsure of what to do (CLUE: that’s why he kept looking at his phone) 

Then he decides to book a flight ticket but he was still relaxed until he found the ring and everything came back to him (CLUE: shaky cam shows his unstable emotions/thoughts all flooding in) and he realizes how badly he wants her back. So he rushes and packs up to fly and win her back (CLUE: Kiss in the background with the lyrics “I'm gonna kiss your lips”) This time through his impulsive decision we can see how his main passion has now become his significant other

EDIT: Based on NCT’s triangular theory of love, I was right OMG
